l be contacted. Criminal and vulnerable sector checks will be required of the successful candidate. Compensation $70,624 per annum (plus benefits and a monthly cell phone allowance) Closes: 13 November, 2024 Chestermere Public Library Chestermere , AB Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
